{"tid":223004,"cid":24,"subCid":0,"title":"[沾水筆]有咩好嘅沾水筆推介","createTime":"2017-04-30T04:13:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-01T05:01:41.000Z","uid":81824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5f552f7e58d720b26854449e0fee2ae47e06a924","tid":223004,"uid":81824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T04:13:22.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n我近排想開始練copperplate<br />\n但係工具個邊無從入手<br />\n<br />\n1)筆桿<br />\n都底係斜好定直好<br />\n利申用右手嘅<br />\n仲有咩牌子會好啲？<br />\n見到有人話speedball都唔錯？<br />\n<br />\n2)墨水<br />\n冇研究過<br />\n有冇啲冇咁多水嘅墨？<br />\n平時玩pilot 隻parallel pen 都覺得啲墨好多水<br />\n<br />\n3)筆尖<br />\n好似都係建議起手用nikko g？<br />\n儲墨器係咪要另購<br />\n仲有如果想寫埋平尖嘅西洋書法(eg gothic)<br />\n邊隻牌子筆尖會好啲？<br />\n會唔會驚筆尖放唔入筆桿<br />\n<br />\n4)紙<br />\n好似都係見人用ipaper/巴川紙？<br />\n<br />\n最後就係要買工具應該去邊到買<br />\n斜筆桿有啲難揾<br />\n直嘅還好<br />\n<br />\n如果有啲咩要留意嘅都不妨講下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e8755a3733d9165a909f58e8a262db28166655f","tid":223004,"uid":81824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T12:31:16.000Z","msg":"係咪開錯台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca27eaa72feae2a465d22a9b87e75e1b94b7ad34","tid":223004,"uid":81824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T16:52:33.000Z","msg":"2 combo"},{"pid":"ffd37c221c209ef45e81a6e878a53ee53402976d","tid":223004,"uid":113275,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T17:56:40.000Z","msg":"1)筆桿<br />\n都底係斜好定直好<br />\n利申用右手嘅<br />\n仲有咩牌子會好啲？<br />\n見到有人話speedball都唔錯？<br />\n<br />\nCopperplate一般用斜，直都可以但比較難適應<br />\nSpeedball麻麻，用Nikko G會過長<br />\n淘寶/外國(e.g.台灣/美國)訂/銅鑼灣pyaar，亦可以睇睇ig<br />\n<br />\n2)墨水<br />\n冇研究過<br />\n有冇啲冇咁多水嘅墨？<br />\n平時玩pilot 隻parallel pen 都覺得啲墨好多水<br />\n<br />\n有專用GE calligraphy ink，但貴<br />\n練習一般用walnut ink，都係pyaar有得賣<br />\n都可以用中國書法墨，但記得買月宮唔好買墨彩，後者垃圾到不得了。一般書局有售。<br />\n一般鋼筆墨水未必得，見過有人用Pelikan 4001 Royal Blue，其他唔sure。<br />\n<br />\n3)筆尖<br />\n好似都係建議起手用nikko g？<br />\n儲墨器係咪要另購<br />\n仲有如果想寫埋平尖嘅西洋書法(eg gothic)<br />\n邊隻牌子筆尖會好啲？<br />\n會唔會驚筆尖放唔入筆桿<br />\n<br />\n因人而異，有人建議用nikko g因為易操控，有人唔建議因為怕習慣左nikko g (較硬尖)以後再用返軟啲GE尖要由頭適應。nikko g唔代表新手，有書法大師用左nikko g幾十年都無問題。<br />\n<br />\n個人認為儲墨器可有可無<br />\n<br />\n易用：nikko/zebra g, brause 66ef<br />\n較軟同幼但新手難控：leonardt principal, gillott 303<br />\n寫大字：Brause Rose<br />\n<br />\n平尖似乎mitchell唔錯，但Pilot Parallel都夠做（同埋可以入鋼筆墨水）<br />\n<br />\n其實筆尖唔貴買哂咁多都得，記得用之前用酒精抺下佢，用完邊隻順手就用住先<br />\n<br />\n一般都放得落<br />\n<br />\n4)紙<br />\n好似都係見人用ipaper/巴川紙？<br />\n<br />\n練習我自己用100gsm A4紙都得，想好少少就買rhodia或者clairefountaine拍紙薄。ipaper/巴川紙無研究<br />\n<br />\n最後就係要買工具應該去邊到買<br />\n斜筆桿有啲難揾<br />\n直嘅還好<br />\n<br />\npyaar"},{"pid":"a1b2038387380b28207bd8e1488dffeca7e85333","tid":223004,"uid":81824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T18:46:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\nSpeedball麻麻，用Nikko G會過長<br />\n淘寶/外國(e.g.台灣/美國)訂/銅鑼灣pyaar，亦可以睇睇ig</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁有咩牌子嘅斜筆桿會好啲？<br />\n例如manuscript？<br />\nig 嘅話有冇link可以提供<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />終於有人理我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n感謝"},{"pid":"e6f937e559e8334d1076e02b3e44261df59305bf","tid":223004,"uid":113275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T19:20:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><br />\nSpeedball麻麻，用Nikko G會過長<br />\n淘寶/外國(e.g.台灣/美國)訂/銅鑼灣pyaar，亦可以睇睇ig</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁有咩牌子嘅斜筆桿會好啲？<br />\n例如manuscript？<br />\nig 嘅話有冇link可以提供<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />終於有人理我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n感謝</blockquote><br />\n其實多數都係人手造無牌子GE<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.johnnealbooks.com/prod_detail_list/s?keyword=oblique\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.johnnealbooks.com%2Fprod_detail_list%2Fs%3Fkeyword%3Doblique&d=A6Q0GQr%2FGmLii1x5qL7rGF0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=ee76dd8b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.johnnealbooks.com/prod_detail_list/s?keyword=oblique</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://huyhoangdao.com/store/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhuyhoangdao.com%2Fstore%2F&d=A6Q0GQr%2FGmLii1x5qL7rGF0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=3b0531ed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://huyhoangdao.com/store/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://thecuriousartisan.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthecuriousartisan.com&d=A6Q0GQr%2FGmLii1x5qL7rGF0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=a74c1f84\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thecuriousartisan.com</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://zh-hk.facebook.com/commerce/products/1136492269766127/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh-hk.facebook.com%2Fcommerce%2Fproducts%2F1136492269766127%2F&d=A6Q0GQr%2FGmLii1x5qL7rGF0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=5ca86e97\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh-hk.facebook.com/commerce/products/1136492269766127/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/hk-en/search?q=oblique+pen+holder\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.etsy.com%2Fhk-en%2Fsearch%3Fq%3Doblique%2Bpen%2Bholder&d=A6Q0GQr%2FGmLii1x5qL7rGF0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=73a6515f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.etsy.com/hk-en/search?q=oblique+pen+holder</a><br />\n<br />\n共通點都係貴<br />\n<br />\n建議淘寶算，打斜桿好多一舊水左右，揀個可調節法蘭GE用住先，有心機練落去再慢慢揀個貴GE"},{"pid":"4ef65b2eb48c437e57d7e64400ac4ab39f1630d1","tid":223004,"uid":81824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T05:01:41.000Z","msg":"感謝回答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}